string-utils provides header-only string manipulation utilities.

Usage:
    find_package(string-utils CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE string-utils::string-utils)

Example:
    #include <string-utils/string_utils.hpp>
    auto parts = str::split("a,b,c", ",");
    auto joined = str::join(parts, ", ");
    auto hex = str::to_hex(data);
    auto lower = str::to_lower("HELLO");
